<h2>Recall</h2>

<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/forums/showthread.php?t=3472091">TUberline Bridge [Done]</a></strong> is a special place where five notable Ubers battlers are ready to take you on during your journey to become the Holder of the Rainbow Tuber! Beat all five in order and you shall win the title!</li>

<li><strong><a href="/forums/showthread.php?t=3465982">Counter That Uber Pokemon Teambuilder</a></strong> is no ordinary teambuilder. The goal of this thread is to build two teams that are supposed to do nothing but beat the other when both are revealed!</li>

<li><strong><a href="/forums/showthread.php?t=3463225">Teambats</a></strong> are basically small, live tournaments, that involve two teams and a special rule of teambuilding. Both teams have a specific amount of time to build their team, and when that time is gone, to the battlefield they go!</li>

<li>Many people find it hard to build an Ubers team. Thus, the <strong><a href="/forums/showthread.php?t=3462087">Ubers CCAT2</a></strong> can be helpful! CCAT is an acronym for Community Create-A-Team, which, like the name suggests, is a team made by the entire Ubers community! In this specific CCAT, we have a special rule: we may not use any form of entry hazard support.</li>
</ul>
